nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.prover
Class ProofBranch

java.lang.Object
  nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.prover.ProofBranch

public class ProofBranch
extends java.lang.Object

this is the class that represents the proof tree, which can be printed after a closed tree has just been proven, meaning that every end of the branch has ended in a contradiction.

Author:
marc
